{"tid":1649213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［10月13號］18區遍地開花事項","createTime":"2019-10-12T14:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T02:49:24.000Z","uid":70403,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"378236a85d61dc20d32599d8b04b93d149e42982","tid":1649213,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"黑警狗察殺我手足，擺明向香港人宣戰！<br />\n1，每個和理<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>至少</strong></span>帶一個玻璃樽！<br />\n捐物資整魔法又好，扔尻班黑警都好！<br />\n有啲嘢揸手都有安全感啲<br />\n2，唔好再遲到，見到少量狗就直接打尻扔尻佢地！<br />\n3，有吉狗車直接燒車！<br />\n4，拆鋪拆辦事處，見到建制拉票直接扔入垃圾桶<br />\n5，哨兵，見到開始有圍捕就散去第二第三集合點<br />\n6，臥底狗，直接殘廢<br />\n7，噴漆塗鴉寫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣</span>冇噴漆就用marker <br />\n8，唔要尻行尻企，搵目標做！起磚，寫文宣都好！<br />\n9，永遠唔好再手軟，見到左膠直接抱走<br />\n10，我愛香港，加油！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Trump仔話點解少咗咁多人上街啊！聽日一定要全城上街！為死去嘅手足討回公道！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警不公，殺警無罪！<br />\n香港人，真係要反抗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e565778bcf698d82977e9a04c101027b8e67c60b","tid":1649213,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:27:02.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1dc07312edc4fe49f9669b7c706f8fa9467be978","tid":1649213,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:33:02.000Z","msg":"求下大家聽日真係出嚟"},{"pid":"f8252ed7af07a837bb60d2351579b0b041545241","tid":1649213,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"dc6cf79de7e174131d3db94dae07c1724158d3e7","tid":1649213,"uid":11628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0547357421e24fade69b67f386e09eb64f331005","tid":1649213,"uid":326930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:35:56.000Z","msg"